thread.title: Brigid & Stuart
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Brigid & Stuart

author: Brigid & Stuart
title: Brigid & Stuart
text: Ryan and Adriana at Nelson Alexander Flemington made a great team and ran a very successful campaign to sell our property in Kensington. They made the process very easy for us, communicated well and promptly. We know they followed up with every potential buyer and they knew all the bidders by name throughout the Auction. Excellent work!
